<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="http://nintendoallstars.w.interia.pl/romlab/crom2cram.htm">http://nintendoallstars.w.interia.pl/ro ... m2cram.htm</a><!-- m -->
<br />which explains the TSROM to TGROM/TNROM. 
<br />
<br />I want to change the SLROM to SGROM, change the 32 pin 128kb CHR ROM chip to 8kb SRAM. Can I use the shcematics on that page? 
<br />I am really a noob and don't (yet) understand the differences between chr-ram, prg-ram, v-ram, s-ram, w-ram stuff, the information on nesdev wiki is insufficient in this kind of matter... Thank you!!

		

