	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Just a question - is there any difference between WRAM and VRAM ? I understand WRAM is Working or PRG RAM, but VRAM ..is CHR RAM?
<br />(like stated for eg. here <!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="http://wiki.nesdev.com/w/index.php/TxROM">http://wiki.nesdev.com/w/index.php/TxROM</a><!-- m --> in the end of the TVROM row in the table)

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


	<hr width="85%" />

	<table width="85%" cellspacing="3" cellpadding="0" border="0" align="center">
	<tr>
