	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td width="10%" nowrap="nowrap">Post subject:&nbsp;</td>
		<td><b></b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />VRAM is any kind of Video RAM, which includes CHR-RAM and Name Table RAM, and palettes.
<br />
<br />WRAM is the same as PRG-RAM.
<br />
<br />I'll add this to the glossary too to make it clearer for future newcomers.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


